     <h2 class="pane-title panel-title">
      <p>
       Learning How to Use ANVILL-LTI
      </p>
     </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pane-content panel-body">
     <p>
      <strong>
       ANVILL-LTI
      </strong>
      (current version)
     </p>
     <ul>
      <li>
       See the
       <strong>
        <a href="https://anvill.uoregon.edu/about/screencasts" target="_blank" title="Screencasts">
         screencasts
        </a>
       </strong>
       above for demonstrations of how to do basic things in ANVILL-LTI.
      </li>
      <li>
       The ANVILL-LTI User's Guide is in two formats, as a .pdf for general access, and as a multi-touch iBook for iOS and MacOS.
       <strong>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B40nlCN1jC9qYnNBWFY0WDZKV0k" target="_blank" title="Download Documentation">
         Download documentation
        </a>
       </strong>
       .
      </li>
     </ul>
